08)--------------RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([__mr_match_number@3], 4), input_partitions=4, schema=[price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_classifier:Utf8, __mr_match_number:UInt64, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean]
09)----------------RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(4), input_partitions=1, schema=[price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_classifier:Utf8, __mr_match_number:UInt64, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean]
10)------------------ProjectionExec: expr=[price_date@1 as price_date, price@2 as price, __mr_classifier@4 as __mr_classifier, __mr_match_number@5 as __mr_match_number, __mr_is_last_match_row@7 as __mr_is_last_match_row], schema=[price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_classifier:Utf8, __mr_match_number:UInt64, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean]
11)--------------------MatchRecognizePatternExec: pattern=Repetition(Symbol(Named("A")), OneOrMore), schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_symbol_A:Boolean;N, __mr_classifier:Utf8, __mr_match_number:UInt64, __mr_match_sequence_number:UInt64, __mr_is_last_match_row:Boolean, __mr_is_included_row:Boolean]
12)----------------------SortExec: expr=[price_date@1 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[false], schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_symbol_A:Boolean;N]
13)------------------------ProjectionExec: expr=[company@0 as company, price_date@1 as price_date, price@2 as price, price@2 > 50 as __mr_symbol_A], schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N, __mr_symbol_A:Boolean;N]
14)--------------------------DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[1], schema=[company:Utf8View;N, price_date:Date32;N, price:Int32;N]

